You will need to download the Models From the model section of this forum.
You will need to make the client reconise that you are adding models to it, there might be tutorials on this - I would recomend downloading a client that already has models in it, Then making it work for your server.
Just add the models into the model folder, Then go into class8.java and add the ints for the custom item, compile and run.
